node.c14nfile-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <span>   <ul class="simplelist">    <li class="member"><span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832">{@link DOMNode::C14N()} - Canonicalize nodes to a string</span></li>   </ul>  </span> </div></div>
