nge of characters from the node</span></li>    <li class="member"><span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832">{@link DOMCharacterData::insertData()} - Insert a string at the specified 16-bit unit offset</span></li>    <li class="member"><span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832">{@link DOMCharacterData::substringData()} - Extracts a range of data from the node</span></li>   </ul>  </span> </div></div>
