n, use <span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832">{@link DOMElement::setAttribute()}</span> instead.       </p>      </p></blockquote>     </dd>       </dl>  </div>   <div class="section">   <h2 class="title">参见</h2>   <p class="para">    <ul class="simplelist">     <li class="member"><a href="http://www.w3.org/TR/2003/WD-DOM-Level-3-Core-20030226/DOM3-Core.html#core-ID-637646024" class="link external">&raquo;&nbsp;W3C specification of Attr</a></li>    </ul>   </p>  </div>  </div>   <h2>目录</h2><ul class="chunklist chunklist_reference"><li>{@link DOMAttr::__construct} — Creates a new DOMAttr object</li><li>{@link DOMAttr::isId} — Checks if attribute is a defined ID</li></ul></div>
